org.point85.workschedule

Class NonWorkingPeriod

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.point85.workschedule.NonWorkingPeriod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<NonWorkingPeriod>

    public class NonWorkingPeriod
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<NonWorkingPeriod>
    Class NonWorkingPeriod represents named non-working, non-recurring periods. For example holidays and scheduled outages such as for preventive maintenance.
